dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Metropolitan Area\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The endeavor\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"over $1bn\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 40 venues\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Autodesk's technology, including Autodesk Construction Cloud and Building Information Modeling (BIM) tools, will play a crucial role in optimizing the venue development process.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crucial role\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue development process\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These tools are expected to streamline project timelines, reduce costs and lower carbon emissions by minimizing the need for new construction materials and energy.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These tools\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"project timelines\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"lower carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"new construction materials\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Modifying existing buildings aligns with LA28's commitment to sustainability, as built environments account for 42% of global carbon emissions, according to non-profit research organization Architecture 2030.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"existing buildings\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"aligns\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"LA28's commitment\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"as built environments\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"42%\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"global carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"non-profit research organization\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"Architecture\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Autodesk's software is a part of our LA28 story: the behind-the-scenes technology that brings our vision of the LA28 Games to life,\\\" LA28 chairperson Casey Wasserman said.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Wasserman\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Wasserman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"our LA28 story\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"the-scenes\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"our vision\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"the LA28 Games\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Together, we will develop the right plan to support 12-15 million ticketed fans over such a short period of time.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right plan\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"12-15 million ticketed fans\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"such a short period\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are honored to have Autodesk on board for the next four years as we embark on our shared commitment in innovative design that can serve as a precedent for many Games to come.\\\"\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"the next four years\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"our shared commitment\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"innovative design\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"a precedent\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"many Games\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The partnership will also aid in designing essential transportation and traffic control elements, which further enhances LA28's resolve for sustainable, effective event planning.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The partnership\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"essential transportation and traffic control elements\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"LA28's resolve\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable, effective event planning\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Autodesk's technology is used every day to design and make a better world, which is why we are thrilled to be LA28's official Design and Make Platform,\\\" added Andrew Anagnost, Autodesk president and CEO.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}, {\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\", \"score\": 0.9999414210774878, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Anagnost\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Anagnost\"}, {\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"LA28's official Design\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"Platform\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"CEO\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our partnership will enable Autodesk software to do more than ever before.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.40859526228561e-16, \"text\": \"Autodesk\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autodesk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our partnership\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together with LA28, we will help prepare Los Angeles for not only a 29-day celebration but also strengthen the greater Los Angeles community by embarking on our shared vision of a more sustainable Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999410297296, \"rank\": 5.379534885379965e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999410297296, \"rank\": 5.379534885379965e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LA28\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"not only a 29-day celebration\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"our shared vision\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"a more sustainable Games\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"